<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Ecobazar</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.css" />
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <style>
        .hover-scale { transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
        .hover-scale:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
        .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in; }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #22c55e, #16a34a);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <%- include('../layouts/headerWithoutUser.ejs') %>

    <!-- Hero Section with Parallax -->
    <div class="relative h-[500px] overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542838132-92c53300491e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3')] bg-cover bg-center bg-fixed"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50"></div>
        <div class="relative container mx-auto px-4 h-full flex items-center justify-center text-center">
            <div data-aos="fade-up">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Fresh From Farm to Your Table</h1>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-8">Delivering Nature's Best Since 2020</p>
                <a href="#story" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full hover:bg-green-600 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Our Journey <i class="fas fa-arrow-down ml-2 animate-bounce"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Our Story Section -->
    <div id="story" class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                Founded in 2020, Ecobazar was born from a simple idea: everyone deserves access to fresh, high-quality produce 
                without leaving their home. What started as a small local delivery service has grown into a comprehensive 
                online marketplace for fresh vegetables, fruits, eggs, meat, and poultry.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Values Grid -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
            <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg hover-scale" data-aos="fade-right">
                <div class="text-green-500 text-5xl mb-6">
                    <i class="fas fa-leaf animate-pulse"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Fresh & Organic</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    We partner with local farmers to bring you the freshest organic produce straight from the farm.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg hover-scale" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="text-green-500 text-5xl mb-6">
                    <i class="fas fa-truck"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Fast Delivery</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Same-day delivery ensures your products reach you at their freshest.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg hover-scale" data-aos="fade-left">
                <div class="text-green-500 text-5xl mb-6">
                    <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Quality Guaranteed</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    We stand behind the quality of every product we deliver.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Product Categories -->
        <div class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 gradient-text" data-aos="fade-up">What We Offer</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover-scale group" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <div class="text-4xl text-green-500 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i class="fas fa-carrot"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Fresh Vegetables</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Locally sourced, seasonal vegetables delivered fresh daily.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover-scale group" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="text-4xl text-green-500 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i class="fas fa-apple-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Fresh Fruits</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Sweet and juicy fruits from trusted orchards.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover-scale group" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="text-4xl text-green-500 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i class="fas fa-egg"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Farm Fresh Eggs</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Free-range eggs from healthy, happy hens.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover-scale group" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="text-4xl text-green-500 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i class="fas fa-drumstick-bite"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Quality Meats</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Premium cuts of meat and fresh poultry products.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sustainability Section -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-inner" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 gradient-text">Our Commitment to Sustainability</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-lg">
                    We're committed to sustainable practices throughout our supply chain. From eco-friendly packaging 
                    to supporting local farmers who use sustainable farming methods, we're doing our part to protect 
                    the environment while delivering quality products to your doorstep.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center bg-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full shadow-md hover-scale">
                        <i class="fas fa-recycle text-green-500 text-2xl mr-3"></i>
                        <span class="font-medium">Eco-Friendly Packaging</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center bg-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full shadow-md hover-scale">
                        <i class="fas fa-seedling text-green-500 text-2xl mr-3"></i>
                        <span class="font-medium">Sustainable Farming</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center bg-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full shadow-md hover-scale">
                        <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart text-green-500 text-2xl mr-3"></i>
                        <span class="font-medium">Community Support</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../layouts/footer.ejs') %>

    <script>
        AOS.init({
            duration: 1000,
            once: true,
            offset: 100
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html> 